article_title: House GOP Wins ObamaCare Subsidies Lawsuit, but the White House Gloats Instead
article_text: Well, the House GOP won a lawsuit over the lawfulness of ObamaCare subsidies, but the White House gloated and said that they’ve won the fight for the past six years.
